      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the info. u mentioned ethnic narratives framing people as outsiders... is that mostly just political stuff or is there a deeper sense of tribalism that makes it hard for the groups to actually work together on things like development or local governance? like, do they just fundamentally clash because of their backgrounds?",
